{"tid":2100982,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[比男人家暴或者出軌更大醜聞！？] Johnny Depp爆Amber Heard喺床上屙屎！！","createTime":"2020-07-09T12:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T02:27:33.000Z","uid":130563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"80999dc778af5713eb2e736f8d6eb70d620580aa","tid":2100982,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:23:26.000Z","msg":"Johnny Depp（尊尼迪普）與前妻Amber Heard（安柏赫德）自離婚後負面新聞不斷，爆出了家暴風波。<br />\n昨日（7/7）Johnny Depp出席法庭控告英國《太陽報》的毀謗官司作證，<br />\n因不滿英國《太陽報》指控他對前妻Amber Heard家暴而導致形象受損，公開了他被妻子家暴後的斷指照，<br />\n控訴Amber Heard多次對他使用肢體暴力。<br />\n隨後，法院卻公開了一段Johnny Depp的暴怒影片，瞬間引起全城熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4uhMoC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4uhMoC.jpg&h=af78e8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJohnny Depp在庭上公布了「斷指照」，憶述在2015年兩人在澳洲吵架時，自己當時很生氣就摔下手機，<br />\n怎料Amber Heard卻把2個伏特加酒瓶扔向他，也因此而令他的手指被碎片割斷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSCy4au.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSCy4au.jpg&h=2e397a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pmA8S3P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpmA8S3P.jpg&h=dfd8dee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來Amber Heard還試過以煙頭燙他的臉頰、在私人飛機上對他揮拳施暴，也用言語攻擊他，取笑他是「fat old man」，但是他卻沒有還手，因為他表示「自己是不會打女人」。<br />\n<br />\nJohnny Depp也提到Amber Heard曾試過在「床上大便」，<br />\n這行為是令他最無法忍受，也超越了容忍的極限，終才決定要跟Amber Heard離婚。"},{"pid":"1378d546b9aa3436b7ada31ee2486e58cbabcec3","tid":2100982,"uid":45138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"Disney:"},{"pid":"cd06938fb95cd414d9e64f87cadbb071a114e4ae","tid":2100982,"uid":230454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:30:08.000Z","msg":"鬼妹版郭羨妮"},{"pid":"0455c17a041209a068af594d582853997b0bee72","tid":2100982,"uid":158372,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:35:25.000Z","msg":"old news<br />\n屌你老母amber狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c485ad5703b642bf9e36b55248810610dfe4b5","tid":2100982,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:22:35.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，幾靚都好核突囉"},{"pid":"27cf2381f6634a2b247f0b50856389e2db88dac5","tid":2100982,"uid":130563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T00:50:59.000Z","msg":"對女名星嚟講俾人知道會屙屎，係咪最大醜聞??"},{"pid":"b710fea1af57d812cab1b5061bf1d64a98e5805d","tid":2100982,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T02:27:33.000Z","msg":"Elon Musk就爽"}]}